{"tid":2036223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國央行：今季經濟將收縮逾20%","createTime":"2020-05-26T10:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:41:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc6aa616d5e2c9e73ecae106a65cd5f2f9b7536","tid":2036223,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1528447_1_20200526174735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1528447_1_20200526174735.jpg&h=0cff2e2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國央行首席經濟學家霍爾丹預計，英國第2季經濟將收縮超過20%。<br />\n<br />\n霍爾丹指，調查顯示支出及企業信心有些企穩，但復蘇情況非常弱，經濟緩慢復蘇的風險較大。<br />\n<br />\n霍爾丹又提到評論負利率時，主要考慮對金融業及經濟信心的影響，央行對距離採取負利率的觀點仍很遙遠。"},{"pid":"cfb91a39444bdee084c3d398a9ca8445b970761e","tid":2036223,"uid":356101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:35:34.000Z","msg":"20%? good news<br />\n升"},{"pid":"55852046f47ad9f0f88ce4e62a48941ecdc2dd10","tid":2036223,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:39:26.000Z","msg":"然後繼續奶共恢復經濟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbff85fe53d6ee4c3f979b91d18ff90e9da05c03","tid":2036223,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:41:52.000Z","msg":"升升升升"}]}